      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5747 - Hammad ibn Isa narrated from Shuayb ibn Yaʿqub from Abu Basir from Abu Abdullah Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) who said:\n\"When a man dies, his eldest son inherits the sword, the saddle, and his personal clothing.\""
